  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
    <h2>Overview:</h2>
     <p>In a judo experiment, you copy your competitor's product and rebrand it as your own.
        It is a quick and simple way to gather feedback, before putting in heavy labor to actually
         build a product. This could mean removing competitor's branding from a product/site.
         This method is particularly effective when selling physical products. </p>


